About SUST IRA

Building Global Bridges
for a Brighter Future

SUST IRA is a pioneering student-led initiative at Shahjalal University of Science and Technology, dedicated to empowering students with global opportunities and international perspectives.

We support students in pursuing higher education abroad, international scholarships, exchange programs, diplomatic engagement, and participation in international competitions â€” growing them into globally conscious, capable future leaders.

Guided by our Constitution, the Association remains firmly unaffiliated with any political party, ensuring every activity aligns with the history, culture, and university regulations.

Mission

01

Connect students interested in international relations with global opportunities and build globally conscious, competent future leaders.

02

Familiarize students with international opportunities and facilities available worldwide.

03

Support participation in global education, higher studies abroad, scholarships, fellowships, and diplomatic programs.

04

Raise student awareness of global competencies and international opportunities continuously.

Vision
